    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable oil leak, while the transmission shifts roughly. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for someone looking for parts or a complete restoration.",
