      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined driving experience, blending consistent performance with a sophisticated aesthetic. Having undergone a rigorous professional assessment, it presents in commendable condition, ensuring both mechanical reliability and exceptional cabin comfort. This is a premier selection for the discerning driver who prioritizes long-term value and engineering integrity.",
